The second aim_ag_texture_town map: AIM_AG_TEXTURE_TOWN2
Another middle-sized map with plenty of good sniping areas as well as close incounters. A decent map for a gungaming server or just a ordinary AIM server.
hope you enjoy it. This newest map is slightly bigger than the last one and is a lot better to play in my opinion.
If you decide to download it and put it on your server, please send me your IP Address so i can come join you! thanks
